desc_short	-----								Mech Marines is a strategic game inspired by Metal Marines (SNES, 1993 by Namco Bandai Games). Build up your island with unique buildings. Defend it at all cost. Attack your opponent with missiles and figure out a leak in the defense to destroy the enemy's bases with your Mech Marines. Equip them with various weapons.							
